<h2>🌿 Meet-n-Greet Scheduled!</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @application.parent_first_name %>,</p>

<p>I hope this email finds you in good health and spirits! Thank you for taking the time to thoughtfully fill out the enrollment application for our <%= @program.start_date.year %>–<%= (@program.start_date + 1.year).year %> Nature Preschool program. <strong>We would love to welcome <%= @application.child_first_name %> and your family to move forward with the next phase of enrollment</strong>.</p>

<h3>Meeting Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Date & Time:</strong> <%= @event.scheduled_at.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
  <li><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @location&.name || 'Forest Hill Park' %></li>
  <% if @location&.address %>
  <li><strong>Address:</strong> <%= @location.address %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Spending time together in the space will give us all an opportunity to explore the environment, answer questions, and make sure the nature preschool feels like a good fit for your family.</p>

<h3>Program Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><%= @program.class_days.presence || 'Days TBD' %>, <%= @program.start_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>–<%= @program.end_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %></li>
  <% if @program.formatted_time_range.present? %>
  <li><%= @program.formatted_time_range %></li>
  <% end %>
  <% tuition = @application.effective_tuition_amount || @program.tuition_amount %>
  <% if tuition.present? %>
  <li>Tuition: $<%= number_with_precision(tuition, precision: 0, delimiter: ',') %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<% if @payment_plans.any? %>
<h3>Payment Options</h3>
<ul>
  <% @application.payment_plan_options.each_with_index do |plan, index| %>
  <li><strong>Option <%= index + 1 %>: <%= plan[:name] %></strong> - <%= plan[:description] %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<% end %>

<p>A <strong>$<%= number_with_precision(@application.effective_enrollment_fee, precision: 0) %> non-refundable enrollment fee</strong> is due upon enrollment to reserve your child's spot in the program. Enrollment is for the full school year.</p>

<p>Please don't hesitate to reach out with any questions. We look forward to connecting with you!</p>

<p>Warmly,<br>
The Nature Preschool Team</p>
